                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "text": "Open the <$Essential Sound$> panel by choosing <$Window$> > <$Essential Sound$>."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "In the <$Browse$> tab, type \"lo fi\" in the search box and press Enter or Return to filter on that search term."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "Click the play button on various music selections to sample them, along with the sequence, without having to add them first to your project."
