                        {
                            "texts": [
                                "Adding music to a sequence automatically adds it to the <$Project$> panel within a new <$Stock Audio Media$> folder. You sampled music on Adobe Stock (featuring tracks from sound library partners Epidemic Sound and Jamendo) and added a selection to your sequence. Licensing the music later is one-click easy."
