                                    ],
                                    "text": "In the <$Timeline$> panel, select the \"Slurping SFX\" clip. Then, in the <$Essential Sound$> panel, click <$Auto-Match$>. Press the <%{KEY.SPACEBAR}%> to play the sequence and hear the added sound effect."
                                },
                                {
                                    "text": "The effect is probably too loud, so select the \"Slurping SFX\" clip again. In the <$Clip Volume$> section of the <$Essential Sound$> panel, drag the slider to the left (around â€“20.0 dB) to make it quieter."
